title: 50 motorsport fans in Germany will get the chance to buy a DTM-inspired Audi A5
text:
50 motorsport fans in Germany will get the chance to buy a DTM-inspired Audi A5 
Published By: DigitalTrends.com - Today 
Audi has introduced a limited-edition version of the A5 whose design is inspired by the heavily-modified RS 5 that competes in touring races...
